milestones.description: David Gower has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (5) in ODIs for ENG, going past Mike Gatting's 4
de Mel has become the top wicket-taker for SL in ODIs with 20 wickets, going past de Silva's 18
Paul Allott has conceded the most runs in an innings (82) in ODIs for ENG, going past Ian Botham's record of 71
Duleep Mendis has broken the record for most ODIs (9) as captain for SL, going past Warnapura
This is the highest match aggregate (619) involving teams England & Sri Lanka in ODIs
de Silva has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (20) for SL, going past Duleep Mendis
David Gower and Ian Gould's 98-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 66 between Fletcher and Chris Old
Guy de Alwis and Ratnayake's 35-run partnership is SL's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 33 between Guy de Alwis and Ratnayake
